dfir_ntfs: an NTFS parser for digital forensics & incident response
(Python 3 only.)

1. Project goals

- Parse $MFT, $UsnJrnl:$J, $LogFile files, extract as much data as possible.
- Parse volumes and volume images.

2. Installation

# pip3 install https://github.com/msuhanov/dfir_ntfs/archive/1.0.0-beta14.tar.gz
or 
# pipenv install -e git+https://github.com/msuhanov/dfir_ntfs.git#egg=dfir_ntfs

